import React from "react";
import Header from "./Header"
import Footer from "./Footer"
import Welcome from "./Welcome"
import { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom'
function Layout() {
   return (
      <React.Fragment>
         <Header />
         <main>
            <Welcome />
            <Outlet />
         </main>
         <Footer />
      </React.Fragment>

   )
}
export default Layout
